article.description: — Dominic Parolin posted 12 points as Lehigh beat Columbia 79-72 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Parolin scores 12 to carry Lehigh past Columbia 79-72
article.linkText: Parolin scores 12 to carry Lehigh past Columbia 79-72
article.story: BETHLEHEM, Pa. -- — Dominic Parolin posted 12 points as Lehigh beat Columbia 79-72 on Tuesday night. Evan Taylor had 18 points and six rebounds for Lehigh (1-4), which ended its season-opening four-game losing streak. Jeameril Wilson added 12 points. Jakob Alamudun had 10 points. Geronimo Rubio De La Rosa had 24 points and six rebounds for the Lions (2-3). Liam Murphy added 10 points and nine rebounds. Patrick Harding had 11 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
